  "instructions": [
    "Heat the claypot over medium heat and add the coconut oil.",
    "Add the grated ginger and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped red chilli and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the curry powder, cumin powder, coriander powder, salt, and black pepper. Stir well.",
    "Add the cooked fried rice and stir well to combine.",
    "Add the coconut milk and stir well to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10-15 minutes or until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Serve hot and garnish with chopped fresh cilantro, if desired."
